data.description: Spacious 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom, Single Family Home with 1 Car Garage located in the desire community of Lake Charleston. Corner unit home featuring: Tile throughout the first floor, eat-in kitchen with Granite Countertops and stainless-Steel appliances, Living, Dining, Family Room, Laminate stairs leading to Master-suite with spacious Master Bathroom with Roman Tub and separate shower. NO CARPET in this home. Relax on your enclosed patio or enjoy all the amenities provided by the association. LOW HOA that includes cable, community pool, tennis, soccer, multiple playgrounds, and basketball courts. Roof and AC installed 2020,
